page.title: 16Clubs In Weston Turville
page.content: Guides In Weston Turville we have a Guide company.It meets every Monday at 6.00p.m until 8.00p.m .At present there are not many Guides in the club. Brownies We have a good Brownie pack in Weston Turville.The pack meets every Tuesday at 6.45p.m until 7.20 p.m at Weston Turville School.There is the maximum amount of Brownies in the Pack at the moment and there is a long waiting list. Youth Clubs Weston Turville youth club takes place on a Tuesday and Wednesday evening.On a Tuesday over 14 year olds go and on a Wednesday evening the younger children go.
